  "detailed_description": "《AbyssalRestaurant》is a cooking simulation as well as a restaurant management game using a physics engine.<br>Players will take on the role of a small restaurant operator and chef in a fantasy world, and experience the process of making a wide variety of food for customers.<br>The game consists of three main modules: receiving customers, making food, and shopping in the market.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/9231d927d98325d6b69c289e71112958.avif?t=1725621676\" width=600 height=98 /></span></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>Nearly 200 different ingredients.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>A dozen types of tastes and scents that change with temperature.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>Customers not only comment on their own food but may also evaluate based on the aromas of food from neighboring tables.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>Food can be cut and processed into any shape, even removing bones from meat cuts.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>Customers of different races and ages each have their own tastes and communication styles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>Freely design each dish.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>Independently customize every item on the restaurant's menu.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>Customers will decide what to eat through intelligent conversations with the owner.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.webp?t=1725621676\" width=30 height=30 /></span>Players can share their culinary creations with their Steam friends.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/acd008a006d83c13e315c1e0c68c6751.webp?t=1725621676\" width=600 height=20 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/7965e58a5ddeaf8f5f892cb000ac986c.webp?t=1725621676\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/7965e58a5ddeaf8f5f892cb000ac986c.poster.avif?t=1725621676\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=216 /></picture></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/acd008a006d83c13e315c1e0c68c6751.webp?t=1725621676\" width=600 height=20 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/66fa5d5f15d58b292804ec8213aa067f.poster.avif?t=1725621676\" width=600 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/66fa5d5f15d58b292804ec8213aa067f.webm?t=1725621676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/66fa5d5f15d58b292804ec8213aa067f.mp4?t=1725621676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/acd008a006d83c13e315c1e0c68c6751.webp?t=1725621676\" width=600 height=20 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/482a8ab1cdbd4444dbda8497949cab3a.poster.avif?t=1725621676\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/482a8ab1cdbd4444dbda8497949cab3a.webm?t=1725621676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/482a8ab1cdbd4444dbda8497949cab3a.mp4?t=1725621676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
